{
  "stem": "8072.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And by the time they wanted to get another stick, I jumped up and ran away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But they didn't chase me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they-- whatever they did, they let me go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they could shoot you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could shoot you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean-- I mean, like I say, they just-- evidently they felt I didn't do such a bad thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they didn't shoot me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, while I was there, and-- the conditions in there-- you got up at 4:00, 5 o'clock in the morning for appel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You stood at attention.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes somebody was missing so you had to stay for hours in attention until they found him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it wouldn't-- it couldn't be-- it wasn't that he was missing, tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He could be dead and didn't show up for the appel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because a lot of people over there at that particular time, they wish they were dead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You weren't a human.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were there, and I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I guess you want to live-- you know, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Many, many a people killed themselves by going to the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- a couple-- one time they had-- I think a couple prisoners were trying to escape, and they were caught.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a public hanging.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they made-- they made everyone line-- everybody get and line up in this place and watch him being hanged.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Watched him be hanged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- so to tell you what-- to tell you what's going to happen to you if you tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They-- they didn't need any reason to-- to hit you or to beat you or to do things like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't need any reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was-- I know-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
